div.p: The Meals Link is available each week Wednesday - Thursday at 12:00pm for the following week. THE LINK SHUTS OFF AT NOON ON THURSDAYS AS THE FOOD ORDER NEEDS TO BE PLACED FOR THE FOLLOWING WEEK THAT DAY.

Complete the Library Request Form link above by 10:00am Monday for Tuesday pickup, and by 10:00am Wednesday for Thursday pickup. Books that are not picked up on Tuesday and Thursday will be delivered the following Monday via the Meal Delivery bus routes.
Homework Packets will be available Thursdays in the cafeteria hallway. If you need your packet picked up, please complete the link above.

div.class: hJDwNd-AhqUyc-uQSCkd jXK9ad D2fZ2 OjCsFc wHaque GNzUNc

div.p: Teachers and Paraprofessionals are available Monday through Friday during school hours. Please contact them via email or whatever program they use with any questions you might have.
Anne Dalbey is available for Technical Support Monday through Friday from 8:00am - 4:00pm.

p.strong: OUR MISSION... The Board of Education of Independent School District #356 is committed to...

div.p: helping individuals acquire the knowledge, skills, and positive attitudes towards self and others that will enable them to solve problems, think creatively, continue learning, and develop maximum potential for leading productive, fulfulling lives in a complex and changing society.
